nt with our team working inside it."}]]}]]}],["$","div","03",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"03"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"We follow your SOPs — and help improve them"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We adapt to your existing workflows. Where we find gaps, we flag them, document the fix, and help you formalize a stronger process. Your billing operation becomes better documented and more consistent over time."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"process-list","children":[["$","div","04",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"04"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"We communicate inside your team's channels"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Slack, Teams, EHR messaging, email — wherever your team already communicates, we show up there. Your staff does not reach out to a vendor. They communicate with a teammate who happens to work remotely."}]]}]]}],["$","div","05",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"05"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"We scale without a new hiring cycle"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"New providers, new locations, seasonal volume changes — we scale immediately without a four-week job posting, without benefits overhead, and without the onboarding gaps that cost practices revenue every time they grow."}]]}]]}],["$","div","06",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"06"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"We report, review, and improve on schedule"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Performance reviews, denial trend analysis, AR aging reports — delivered to your leadership on a consistent schedule. Not reactive reports after something goes wrong. Proactive visibility so decisions get made before problems compound."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}